%^BOLD%^%^MAGENTA%^%^ULINE%^Spellscar Mystery%^RESET%^

Primal and chaotic, the raw power of magic gives you all the direction you require.

%^BOLD%^MAGENTA%^Revelations:%^RESET%^
( 1) Mystic Bolt           : Innate Ability
( 5) Animate Primal Forces : Summon an elemental companion
(10) Primal Resistance     : Scaling resistance to acid/cold/fire/electricity
(15) Mystic Null           : +2 to saves vs spells
(21) Magic Penetration     : +4 to dispel magic rolls
(31) Final Revelation      : Gain the Spellscar metamagic feat

%^BOLD%^%^MAGENTA%^Class Skills%^RESET%^: academics, perception, survival

%^BOLD%^%^MAGENTA%^Bonus Spells%^RESET%^: armor, resist energy, dispel magic, true form, siphon magic, globe of invulnerability, spell turning, spellscar, imprisonment